        <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl">Everything you need to make your website work for you</p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">We deliver web design services that create a lasting impression for your business. Your website is often the first point of contact with your audience, and we ensure it makes a powerful impact and is user friendly.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-none">
        <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3">
          
            <div class="flex flex-col">
            <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-2xl leading-7 text-white">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#ff9a02" class="w-16 h-16">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12 2.25c-5.385 0-9.75 4.365-9.75 9.75s4.365 9.75 9.75 9.75 9.75-4.365 9.75-9.75S17.385 2.25 12 2.25zm-2.625 6c-.54 0-.828.419-.936.634a1.96 1.96 0 00-.189.866c0 .298.059.605.189.866.108.215.395.634.936.634.54 0 .828-.419.936-.634.13-.26.189-.568.189-.866 0-.298-.059-.605-.189-.866-.108-.215-.395-.634-.936-.634zm4.314.634c.108-.215.395-.634.936-.634.54 0 .828.419.936.634.13.26.189.568.189.866 0 .298-.059.605-.189.866-.108.215-.395.634-.936.634-.54 0-.828-.419-.936-.634a1.96 1.96 0 01-.189-.866c0-.298.059-.605.189-.866zm2.023 6.828a.75.75 0 10-1.06-1.06 3.75 3.75 0 01-5.304 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 5.25 5.25 0 007.424 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
