            <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
              <p class="flex-auto">We know that complex websites can deter visitors. That's why we prioritize user-friendly interfaces, making it easy for your audience to find what they need.

              </p>
              
            </dd>
          </div>
          

          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-2xl leading-7 text-white">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#ff9a02" class="w-16 h-16">
                <path d="M10.5 18.75a.75.75 0 000 1.5h3a.75.75 0 000-1.5h-3z" />
