              </svg>
              
                  
             <span class="font-bold">Effective Content</span>
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
              <p class="flex-auto">We focus on creating content that engages your audience and drives results. Whether it's compelling copy or eye-catching visuals, we ensure your message resonates with visitors.</p>
              
            </dd>
          </div>
          

          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-2xl leading-7 text-white">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#ff9a02" class="w-16 h-16">
                <path d="M18.375 2.25c-1.035 0-1.875.84-1.875 1.875v15.75c0 1.035.84 1.875 1.875 1.875h.75c1.035 0 1.875-.84 1.875-1.875V4.125c0-1.036-.84-1.875-1.875-1.875h-.75zM9.75 8.625c0-1.036.84-1.875 1.875-1.875h.75c1.036 0 1.875.84 1.875 1.875v11.25c0 1.035-.84 1.875-1.875 1.875h-.75a1.875 1.875 0 01-1.875-1.875V8.625zM3 13.125c0-1.036.84-1.875 1.875-1.875h.75c1.036 0 1.875.84 1.875 1.875v6.75c0 1.035-.84 1.875-1.875 1.875h-.75A1.875 1.875 0 013 19.875v-6.75z" />
              </svg>
              
                  
             <span class="font-bold">Scalable Solutions
            </span>
            </dt>
            <dd class="mt-4 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
              <p class="flex-auto">Our designs are built to grow with your business. Whether you're a small startup or an established enterprise, our websites are flexible and scalable to accommodate your future needs.</p>
             
            </dd>
          </div>
          

          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <dt class="flex items-center gap-x-3 text-2xl leading-7 text-white">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#ff9a02" class="w-16 h-16">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.25 6.75a3.75 3.75 0 117.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 01-7.5 0zM15.75 9.75a3 3 0 116 0 3 3 0 01-6 0zM2.25 9.75a3 3 0 116 0 3 3 0 01-6 0zM6.31 15.117A6.745 6.745 0 0112 12a6.745 6.745 0 016.709 7.498.75.75 0 01-.372.568A12.696 12.696 0 0112 21.75c-2.305 0-4.47-.612-6.337-1.684a.75.75 0 01-.372-.568 6.787 6.787 0 011.019-4.38z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
